Trolls in Rathe...decent, but boring<br>
<br>
Overthere, too damn boring, considering you've probably <br>
spent 10 levels there already <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  and not very good exp<br>
<br>
CC Geonids. Great place, but dont loose more exp than to dubious (You can fix faction from there by doing the first part of Phenocryst focus quest several times if you find you really want to do the quest later)<br>
<br>
My favourite for this level: Dreadlands, go for Drolvarg Ragers if possible.<br>
Now, the clue for efficient leveling in 45 here, is to solo AND grab all the clarity / clarity 2 you can. BEG! DONATE! WHATEVER!<br>
