<br>
There are 6 spawns in the dock area, 4 on Kaladimcitizens faction and 2 on Guards faction.<br>
<br>
I had a Kindly Guards faction, so I killed all of these.<br>
<br>
I wish I'd done this as early as 45 (did 47 here), but when I dropped by a couple of times, there was always droods here.<br>
<br>
I used air pet, pulled with Shock of swords, let pet attack, then nuked once more with shock as fast as possible (often pet would stun them, and I got 2nd nuke off at once)<br>
They'll then start running, or should I say walking away veeery slowly and pet whacks them fast.<br>
<br>
The spawn time is such that you can easily take all 6 when you have staggered the spawns reasonably.<br>
<br>
I pulled the 2 on docks ashore, and the 2 in the huts, well I just sat down outside and they jumped me when they spawned.<br>
<br>
All of these green out at 48, figure I'll do 48 in DL. <p>Appren Hightowerr <BR>
Gnome Magician 48 <BR>
Member of Acolytes Reborn <BR>
Tholuxe Paells <BR>

